               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18460330-name-1035" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18460330-name-1035" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460330-name-1035" type="surname" value="KING"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460330-name-1035" type="given" value="MARY ANN"></interp>MARY ANN KING</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of George King—we life in Essex-court, Borough—on the 18th of March, about nine o'clock in the morning, the prisoner came to our house for a bed—I missed her at five o'clock the next morning—I also missed my shawl, counterpane, my cloak, and 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. that was in my pocket—these are the articles I missed.</p>
