               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I went to lodge at Mrs. King's; I gave her half-a-sovereign for the clothes, and then she asked me to give her the money back again; she wanted me to go on the town to get money for her, and the pawned my frock.</p>
